                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2003-11-11</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This is a great book that will hold your interest, even if you are not a golf junkie. Many of the characters provide laugh out loud dialogue and are put into situations that are very memorable. <P>This is a book that is long enough to last 2 trans continental flights and good enough to let someone borrow. All of McAlister's books have been great and I can hardly wait for the next Caminetti installment. Enjoy....</span>
                  
              
